<li id="cite_note-S121-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-S121_12-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-S121_12-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#Schilling">Schilling 2002</a>, pp. 121–123</span></li>
